disableDozeText:
Disabling Doze mode for {Config.appName} can help ensure your wallet is always synced or nearly synced. Doze mode prevents background syncing from firing consistently, especially if you are not using your phone, to save battery.{

}To disable Doze mode, simply click the link below, then select 'All Apps' from the dropdown.{

}Next, scroll down to find {Config.appName}, click it, then choose 'Don"t optimize'.{

}Click done, and you are finished!{

}
